e called Judges, who combine the duties of judge, jury and executioner to deliver a brutal brand of swift justice. But even the top-ranking Judge, Dredd, discovers that taking down Ma-Ma isn’t as easy as it seems in this explosive adaptation of the hugely popular comic series."},"name":"English","iso_639_1":"en","iso_3166_1":"US","english_name":"English"},{"data":{"title":"Dredd - Il giudice dell'apocalisse","runtime":95,"tagline":"Il giudizio sta arrivando.","homepage":"https://eaglepictures.com/dredd-il-giudice-dell-apocalisse.html","overview":"America del futuro, la metropoli Mega City è invasa dal caos e dalla criminalità. Le forze dell’ordine, i Giudici, possiedono 3 poteri: arrestare, giudicare e giustiziare. Dredd è il giudice più duro e spietato ed è chiamato a risolvere l’ultimo dei tanti problemi che flagella la città: una droga pericolosa che fa vivere la realtà ad una frazione della sua velocità normale, la “Slo-Mo”. Durante l’addestramento del giudice Anderson i due vengono a conoscenza di un delitto in un quartiere dove i colleghi non osano minimamente entrare, una cittadella costruita su 200 piani d’altezza sotto il controllo della signora della droga Ma-Ma e del suo spietato clan. Mentre il numero dei caduti aumenta Dredd e Anderson si trovano senza via d'uscita ed in lotta contro le probabilità di una loro sopravvivenza."},"name":"Italiano","iso_639_1":"it","iso_3166_1":"IT","english_name":"Italian"},{"data":{"title":"","runtime":95,"tagline":"Ankläger. Richter. Henker.","homepage":"http://www.dredd-film.de/","overview":"Das zukünftige Amerika ist verstrahltes Brachland. An der Ostküste liegt Mega City One - eine riesige, gewalttätige Metropole wo Kriminelle die chaotischen Straßen beherrschen. Die einzige Kraft der Ordnung liegt bei den städtischen Polizisten genannt \"Judges\" die sich durch die kombinierten Kräfte der Richter, Jury und Henker auszeichnen. Bekannt und in der ganzen Stadt gefürchtet. Dredd ist der höchste Richter, mit der Aufgabe die Stadt von der neusten Plage zu befreien - einer gefährlichen Drogen Epidemie, die Nutzer von \"Slo-Mo\" erleben Wirklichkeit zu einem Bruchteil ihrer normalen Geschwindigkeit. Während eines routinemäßigen Tages bei der Arbeit wurde Dredd zugewiesen Cassandra Anderson zu trainieren,  eine Anfängerin mit mächtigen psychischen Fähigkeiten dank einer genetischen Mutation. Ein abscheuliches Verbrechen ruft sie in eine Gegend, wo Judges sich nur selten hinwagen - einem Slum, kontrolliert von Prostituierten veränderten Drogen Lord Ma-Ma und ihr rücksichtsloser Clan."},"name":"Deutsch","iso_639_1":"de","iso_3166_1":"DE","english_name":"German"},{"data":{"title":"השופט דראד","runtime":0,"tagline":"הוא השופט, המושבעים והמוציא לפועל.","homepage":"","overview":"דראד לוקח אותנו לרחובות הפרועים של מגה סיטי, נווה המדבר היחיד של הסביליזציה על כדור הארץ המקולל. השופט דרד הוא שופט רחוב שכל הפושעים מפחדים ממנו, יש לו את הסמכות, לאכוף את החוק, לשפוט, להטיל על הנאשם גזר דין ואף להוציא אותו להרוג במידת הצורך."},"name":"עִבְרִית","iso_639_1":"he","iso_3166_1":"IL","english_name":"Hebrew"},{"data":{"title":"","runtime":95,"tagline":"En mand - En nævning - En dommer.","homepage":"","overview":"I en hærget fremtid, hvor befolkningen er samlet i enorme Mega-byer, sørger de såkaldte 'dommere' for at opretholde lov og orden - ofte med dødelige midler. Den mest frygtede dommer og bøddel i Mega-City One er Dredd. Under en rutinemission fanges han med den synske rekrut Cassandra i et berygtet 200 etagers højhus, hvorfra narkobaronessen Ma-Ma forsyner slummen med det dødsensfarlige stof slo-mo."},"name":"Dansk","iso_639_1":"da","iso_3166_1":"DK","english_name":"Danish"},{"data":{"title":"","runtime":96,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"Det framtida Amerika är ett öde land. Längs med östkusten, från Boston till Washington DC, sträcker sig Mega City One, en våldsam plats där de kriminella regerar på gatorna. Den enda officiella makten finns hos stadspolisen, de så kallade judges, som är en kombination av domare, jury och bödel. Den mest fruktade av dem är Dredd. Det är till honom det livsfarliga uppdraget går - att befria staden från drogen Slo-Mo, en drog som för användarna att uppleva verkligheten i ett tempo som bara är en bråkdel av det normala. For att konfrontera fienden måste Dredd ta sig in i grannskapet där han mot alla odds tvingas slåss för sin överlevnad."},"name":"svenska","iso_639_1":"sv","iso_3166_1":"SE","english_name":"Swedish"},{"data":{"title":"Судья Дредд","runtime":95,"tagline":"«Я — закон»","homepage":"","overview":"Будущее не столь красочно и великолепно, каким его представляют современные люди. Через несколько столетий человечество окажется на грани самоуничтожения, захлёбываясь в кровавых преступлениях, смертельных грехах и беспорядочных убийствах. Старую систему правосудия будет невозможно использовать — анархия, всеобщие беспорядки вынуждают ещё сохранившуюся власть, тем не менее, потерявшую всякий авторитет и легитимность, пойти на отчаянные крайние меры и ввести институт Судей — универсальных полицейских, правоприменителей, а по совместительству — и прокуроров, которые упростили бы весь процесс задержания, следствия и судебных тяжб, совмещая в одном лице все должности блюстителей и защитников правопорядка."},"name":"Pусский","iso_639_1":"ru","iso_3166_1":"RU","english_name":"Russian"},{"data":{"title":"Dredd","runtime":95,"tagline":"Le jugement est proche.","homepage":"http://dreddthemovie.com/index.html","overview":"Dans un avenir proche, les États-Unis ne sont plus qu’un immense désert irradié. Mega City One est une métropole tentaculaire rongée par le vice. La seule forme d’autorité restante est représentée par les juges, une police urbaine qui cumule toutes les fonctions : flic, juge et bourreau. Une nouvelle drogue se propage, la Slo-Mo, qui permet de percevoir la réalité au ralenti. Sa distribution est contrôlée par Ma-Ma, ancienne prostituée, devenue baronne de la drogue. Dredd, le juge ultime, va se voir assigner une mission dans les environs de la tour de Ma-Ma et va devoir s’y confronter."},"name":"Français","iso_639_1":"fr","iso_3166_1":"FR","english_name":"French"},{"data":{"title":"Dredd","runtime":95,"tagline":"Juez. Jurado. Ejecutor.","homepage":"","overview":"En un futuro cercano, Norteamérica se ha convertido en un páramo asolado por la radiactividad. Una única y gran megalópolis se extiende a lo largo de la costa este: Mega City 1. Esta inmensa y violenta urbe cuenta con una población de más de 800 millones de personas, cada una de las cuales es un infractor en potencia. Los encargados de acabar con el caos e imponer el orden son unos individuos que actúan a la vez como agentes de la ley, jueces, jurados y verdugos. Al frente de ellos está Dredd (Karl Urban), una leyenda viva de la justicia que vive entregado por entero a hacer cumplir la ley. En una misión aparentemente rutinaria junto a Cassandra Anderson (Olivia Thrilby), una juez novata dotada de grandes habilidades psíquicas, se disponen a investigar un homicidio en un peligroso rascacielos de 200 pisos de altura, controlado por el clan de la despiadada Ma-Ma (Lena Headley)."},"name":"Español","iso_639_1":"es","iso_3166_1":"ES","english_name":"Spanish"},{"data":{"title":"დრედი 3D","runtime":0,"tagline":"სამართალი გვიახლოვდება","homepage":"","overview":"დანაშაულით სავსე მომავლის ქალაქი სადაც პოლიციას აქვს უფლება იყოს მოსამართლე, ნაფიცი მსაჯული და ჯალათი, პოლიციელების ჯგუფები ემზადება რეალობის შემცვლელი ნარკოტიკის გამსაღებელი ნარკოდილერების გასანადგურებლად"},"name":"ქართული","iso_639_1":"ka","iso_3166_1":"GE","english_name":"Georgian"},{"data":{"title":"Hội Thẩm Phán","runtime":0,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"Tương lai nước Mỹ bị nhấn chìm trong bạo lực, băng đảng làm chủ đường phố và các Mega City. Chỉ có một thế lực duy nhất dám đứng lên chống lại thế giới tội phạm này, đó chính là \"Hội Thẩm Phán\". Họ là những cảnh sát kỳ cựu được trao quyền tự quyết định và tự hành xử. Trong đó, Dredd (Karl Urban thủ vai) là thẩm phán tối cao, và là cái tên mà băng đảng phải khiếp sợ mỗi khi nhắc đến.Trong thế giới tội phạm, tú bà Ma-Ma (Lena Headey đóng) vừa là trùm xã hội đen vừa là đầu nậu cung cấp ma túy mới, gây ảo giác \"chậm\" mà giới trẻ đang nghiện. Dredd cùng với lính mới Caassandra Anderson (Olivia Thrilby thủ vai), sẽ dấn thân vào những khu ổ chuột, đương đầu với các băng đảng xã hội đen và tham gia cuộc chiến bất tận ..."},"name":"Tiếng Việt","iso_639_1":"vi","iso_3166_1":"VN","english_name":"Vietnamese"},{"data":{"title":"Dredd","runtime":95,"tagline":"O julgamento está a chegar","homepage":"","overview":"Num vulgar dia de trabalho, Dredd é escolhido para treinar e avaliar Cassandra Anderson (Olivia Thirlby), uma novata que possui poderosas capacidades psíquicas devido a uma mutação genética. Um terrível crime leva-os a um bairro onde os juízes raramente se aventuram a entrar - um edifício de 200 andares controlado pelo clã de Ma-Ma (Lena Headey), uma prostituta que controla o trafico da droga. Quando Dredd e Cassandra capturam um elemento do círculo privado do clã, Ma-Ma assume o controlo da acção e inicia uma guerra suja e cruel contra os juízes, deixando claro que nada a vai impedir de proteger o seu império. Rodeados por um cada vez maior número de inimigos, e sem fuga à vista, Dredd e Anderson são obrigados a entrar numa impiedosa batalha pela sobrevivência."},"name":"Português","iso_639_1":"pt","iso_3166_1":"PT","english_name":"Portuguese"},{"data":{"title":"دريد","runtime":0,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"تدور أحداث الفيلم في إطار خيال علمي في المستقبل البعيد، حول مدينة يسيطر عليها جهاز الشرطة الذي أصبح في ذات الوقت قاضي وجلاد وهيئة محلفين، محتكرًا كل السلطات في يده، فيتولى أحد الضباط برفقة زميلته القضاء على العنف والفساد بالمدينة، وضبط عصابة تتاجر في مخدر خطير محرف للواقع."},"name":"العربية","iso_639_1":"ar","iso_3166_1":"SA","english_name":"Arabic"},{"data":{"title":"","runtime":95,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"Dredd neemt ons mee naar de ruige straten van Mega City One, een eenzame oase van quasi-beschaving op de vervloekte Aarde. Judge Dredd is de meest gevreesde rechter van de Straatrechters, met de macht om de wet te handhaven, overtreders te bestraffen en hen – indien nodig – ter plekke te executeren."},"name":"Nederlands","iso_639_1":"nl","iso_3166_1":"NL","english_name":"Dutch"},{"data":{"title":"Yargıç Dredd","runtime":0,"tagline":"Hüküm vakti geliyor.","homepage":"","overview":"Dünyanın Atom Çağı'na girdiği gelecekte insanlar megapollerde yaşamaya başlamıştır ve suça karşı acıması olmayan polis güçleri suçlu potansiyali gördüğü her insanı acımasızca cezalandırmaktadır. Gelecekteki Amerika radyasyona maruz kalmış çorak bir ülkedir. Boston’dan Washington DC’ye kadar tüm Doğu Yakası’nda suçluların kaotik sokaklara hükmettiği bir metropolis olan Mega Şehir Bir vardır. Düzene müdahale edebilen tek kuvvet “Hakimler” denilen şehir polisleridir. Hakimler’in hüküm verme, yargılama ve anında cezai yaptırımda bulunma güçleri vardır. Bütün şehir tarafından bilinen ve korkulan Dredd (Karl Urban) son Hakim’dir. Şehri son felaketinden yani tehlikeli bir uyuşturucu salgınından kurtarmakla görevlendirilmiştir. Rutin bir iş gününde, Dredd’e genetic mutasyon sayesinde güçlü fiziksel yeteneklere sahip olan Cassandra Anderson (Olivia Thirlby) isimli çaylağı eğitme ve değerlendirme görevi verilir..."},"name":"Türkçe","iso_639_1":"tr","iso_3166_1":"TR","english_name":"Turkish"},{"data":{"title":"","runtime":95,"tagline":"Dzień sądu nadchodzi.","homepage":"","overview":"W niedalekiej przyszłości prawo egzekwują sędziowie. Sami ścigają przestępców, wydają wyroki i wymierzają kary. Losy podejrzanych są wyłącznie w ich rękach. Nic więc dziwnego, że sędziowie budzą lęk i nienawiść w przestępczym świecie. W największej światowej metropolii Mega City One, za szczególnie bezwzględnego wobec bandytów uchodzi sędzia Dredd. Jego wyroki są surowe ale sprawiedliwe, a winnego zawsze spotyka kara. Niejeden przestępca dużo by dał za głowę Dredda. Tymczasem w olbrzymim mieszkalnym gmachu o nazwie Peach Tree Block wybuchają zamieszki. Wszyscy wiedzą, że jest  to najbardziej niebezpieczne miejsce w mieście. Budynkiem włada Ma-Ma stojąca na czele bezwzględnego gangu handlarzy narkotyków. Wezwany do zamieszek Dredd jak zwykle pewnie wkracza do akcji. Szybko jednak okazuje się, że tym razem znalazł się w pułapce."},"name":"Polski","iso_639_1":"pl","iso_3166_1":"PL","english_name":"Polish"},{"data":{"title":"特警判官","runtime":95,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"　　未来世界，地球爆发了惨绝人寰的核战争。曾经显赫一时的超级大国美利坚合众国，也在连番的自戕战争中灰飞烟灭。现如今，以当初华盛顿等地为中心，高高的围墙将北核污染的大地隔绝在外，仅存的8亿人类生活在这名为超级城市一号的封闭空间内。只是人类从来不曾吸取教训，各种恶性犯罪层出不穷，鲜血燃红大地。在此期间，名为“特警判官”的一群暴力机器得到确立，冷酷干练的Dredd（Karl Urban 饰）即是其中一员。他接手新人卡珊卓·安德森（Olivia Thirlby 饰）的培训评审工作，与之异同调查城市中似乎永无止境的恶性案件。在此期间，超级罪恶女头目“马-马”（Lena Headey 饰）浮出水面，成为这对特警搭档面前最大的对手……"},"name":"普通话","iso_639_1":"zh","iso_3166_1":"CN","english_name":"Mandarin"},{"data":{"title":"","runtime":95,"tagline":"Az ítélet közeleg","homepage":"http://www.dreddthemovie.com/index.html","overview":"A lidércnyomásos jövőben tombol a bűnözés, bírók, rendőrök és ítéletvégrehajtók próbálják megvédeni az ártatlan polgárokat. Dredd bíró, a törvényesség elkötelezett híve mindent megtesz, hogy fenntartsa a rendet és a békét. Karl Urban megmutatja hogyan is kell hitelesen előadni a képregények legkeményebb, de leginkább legkönyörtelenebb igazságosztóját, aki még Sly Dredd bíróját is keresztbe lenyeli, miközben egy maroklőfegyverrel lebont egy komplett tömbházat."},"name":"Magyar","iso_639_1":"hu","iso_3166_1":"HU","english_name":"Hungarian"},{"data":{"title":"Dredd","runtime":95,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"Děj se odehrává v budoucnosti, kdy je Amerika jen sežehnutá prázdná planina. Na jejím východním pobřeží se táhne od Bostonu až po Washington DC obrovské měso „Mega City One“, rozsáhlá, násilnická metropole, kde kriminálníci vládnou chaosu na ulicích. Na pořádek v ulicích města dohlížejí policisté zvaní „Soudci“, kteří mají oprávnění jednat jako soudce, porota i popravčí. Známý a po celém městě obávaný nejvyšší soudce Dredd je přivolán k vypořádání se s ničivou pohromou v podobě nové drogy „Slo-Mo“, která umožňuje uživatelům prožívání reality za zlomek jejího skutečného času."},"name":"Český","iso_639_1":"cs","iso_3166_1":"CZ","english_name":"Czech"},{"data":{"title":"Dredd","runtime":95,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"Tulevaisuuden kaupungit ovat yhtä suurta kaatopaikkaa, rikollisuus kukoistaa ja tavikset ovat kovilla. Oikeuslaitos käyttää poliiseinaan tuomareita, joiden oikeudentajua on vaikea horjutaa, ja joiden harkinnalla tuomioita jaellaan nopsaan. Nopeus on valttia kun vain muutamaan prosenttiin hälytyksistä pystytään vastaamaan. Yhteen tällaiseen hälytykseen vastaavat Dredd ja keltanokka, mutanttimaiset meedionkyvyt omaava, Anderson. Parivaljakko päätyy lohduttomaan lähiöön, 200 -kerrosta korkeaan betonitaloon, jonka uumenissa majailee odottamaton uhka. Julma ja hulluuden rajoilla horjuva Ma-Ma hallitsee paitsi valtaisaa rikollisjoukkoa, myös uutta muotihuumetta - Slow Mo:ta. Dredd ja Anderson joutuvat taistelemaan tiensä eteenpäin kerros kerrokselta saadakseen käsiinsä ylimmässä kerroksessa asuvan rikollispomon."},"name":"suomi","iso_639_1":"fi","iso_3166_1":"FI","english_name":"Finnish"},{"data":{"title":"เดร็ด คนหน้ากากทมิฬ","runtime":95,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"หลังอารยธรรมโลกล่มสลาย อเมริกา อดีตประเทศมหาอำนาจเหลือเมืองเพียงแห่งเดียว คือ เมกาซิตีวัน ที่ตั้งอยู่บริเวณที่เคยเป็นที่ตั้งของเมืองบอสตันจรดวอชิงตันดีซี เมกาซิตีวันเป็นเมืองแห่งความรุนแรงที่มีอาชญากรเป็นผู้ปกครอง คนกลุ่มเดียวที่เหลืออยู่พอที่จะใช้อำนาจปราบปรามได้คือตำรวจที่เรียกว่าตุลาการ ซึ่งมีสิทธิ์ในการพิพากษา ว่าความ ไปจนถึงประหารชีวิตแบบทันทีทันใด\r เดร็ดด์ (คาร์ล เออร์เบิน) ตุลาการผู้สร้างความหวาดกลัวให้แก่เหล่าอาชญากรมากที่สุดคนหนึ่ง ได้รับคำสั่งให้ฝึก คาสซานดรา แอนเดอร์สัน (โอลิเวีย เธิร์ลบี) เจ้าหน้าที่คนใหม่ที่มีพลังจิตอันเป็นผลมาจากการกลายพันธุ์ของยีน ทั้งคู่ต้องเร่งหาวิธีรับมือกับการแพร่ระบาดอย่างรุนแรงของยาเสพติดขนานใหม่ที่เรียกว่าสโล-โม ซึ่งมีผลให้ผู้เสพรับรู้การเคลื่อนไหวของสิ่งรอบตัวผิดจากความเร็วปกติ ผู้ที่อยู่เบื้องหลังยาร้ายแรงนี้ก็ไม่ใช่ใครอื่น นอกจากอดีตโสเภณีที่ผันตัวเป็นเจ้าแม่ยาเสพติดอย่าง มา-มา (ลีนา เฮดีย์) ผู้ยิ่งใหญ่แห่งถิ่นเสื่อมโทรมที่ไม่มีตุลาการคนไหนกล้าเข้าใกล้"},"name":"ภาษาไทย","iso_639_1":"th","iso_3166_1":"TH","english_name":"Thai"},{"data":{"title":"Dredd","runtime":0,"tagline":"Dredd","homepage":"","overview":"I en futuristisk by, hvor politiet fungerer som dommer, jury og bøddel, forsøker en politiman og hans lærling å stoppe en narkotikabande fra å spre et nytt dop med virkelighetsforandrende egenskaper."},"name":"Norsk","iso_639_1":"no","iso_3166_1":"NO","english_name":"Norwegian"},{"data":{"title":"","runtime":0,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"Zem, nie príliš vzdialená budúcnosť. Mega City One je gigantická metropola v polorozpadnutom srdci zvyškov toho, čo kedysi bývalo Amerikou. Jej poväčšine drogovo závislí zúbožení obyvatelia príšerne trpia vďaka novej droge, ktorá dokáže extrémne spomaliť vnímanie reality, akoby ste ho prežívali nekonečne pomaly. Jedine Sudcovia môžu a smú bojovať na tomto Bohom zabudnutom mieste všetkými dostupnými prostriedkami proti kriminalite. Dredd, najobávanejší a najradikálnejší zo všetkých Sudcov, je skalopevne rozhodnutý zbaviť mesto tej najväčšej to všetkých pliag, a tak sa spolu s mladou regrútkou Cassandrou Andersonovou, pustí do nerovného a zdanlivo beznádejného boja s vražednou pološialenou mafiánkou menom Ma-Ma – drsnou narkobarónkou, ktorá kruto a neohrozene vládne najväčšiemu z miestnych slumov. Keď sa Dreddovi a Andersonovej podarí chytiť jedného z členov jej zvlčilého klanu, rozpúta Ma-Ma nemilosrdnú vojnu pre ochranu – alebo skôr za záchranu - svojho impéria."},"name":"Slovenčina","iso_639_1":"sk","iso_3166_1":"SK","english_name":"Slovak"},{"data":{"title":"","runtime":95,"tagline":"Η κρίση έρχεται.","homepage":"","overview":"Σε ένα εφιαλτικό μέλλον όπου η Γη έχει καταστραφεί από ατομικά όπλα, οι εναπομείναντες άνθρωποι ζουν σε Mega-Cities που την προστασία τους έχουν αναλάβει οι Δικαστές, μια αστυνομική δύναμη με εξουσία να χρησιμοποιεί βία. Έξω από τις πόλεις, στην ραδιενεργή Καταραμένη Γη, ζουν μεταλλαγμένοι. Ο Δικαστής Dredd στην Mega-City One, σε συνεργασία με την ασκούμενη Κασσάνδρα Άντερσον αναλαμβάνουν να εντοπίσουν και να εξαρθρώσουν μια τρομοκρατική οργάνωση που υπό την αρχηγία της Ma-Ma διακινούν το Slo-Mo, μια ναρκωτική ουσία που αλλάζει την πραγματικότητα."},"name":"ελληνικά","iso_639_1":"el","iso_3166_1":"GR","english_name":"Greek"},{"data":{"title":"저지 드레드","runtime":0,"tagline":"세상을 구원할 심판자가 온다!","homepage":"","overview":"먼 미래, 세상은 폐허가 되고 사람들은 거대한 도시 메가 시티에 모여 삶을 연명한다. 이곳은 정부도 통치자도 없는 곳으로 모든 범죄는 무방비로 노출 된다. 하지만 메가 시티에도 법을 집행하기 위한 자들이 있으니 그들을 저지 - 심판자라 부르며 그 중 가장 뛰어난 자가 바로 심판자 드레드이다. 드레드는 초능력을 소유한 신입 파트너 앤더슨과 함께 모든 불법의 근원지 피치트리로 향한다. 200층의 위용을 자랑하는 제국은 그들을 맞이해 건물을 봉쇄하고 전쟁을 준비하는데..."},"name":"한국어/조선말","iso_639_1":"ko","iso_3166_1":"KR","english_name":"Korean"},{"data":{"title":"Дред","runtime":95,"tagline":"Правосъдието идва","homepage":"","overview":"В един футуристичен град, изпълнен с насилие и агресия, където полицията има неограничени правомощия да действа като съдия и екзекутор, едно легендарно ченге се съюзява с неопитния си нов партньор, за да спре безскрупулна престъпна банда, която търгува с наркотици за изменение на действителността.  За разлика от обикновените полицейски служители, Дред и останалите улични съдии имат правото да осъждат престъпниците на момента - и ако присъдата е смърт - да ги екзекутират директно на мястото на което са задържани."},"name":"български език","iso_639_1":"bg","iso_3166_1":"BG","english_name":"Bulgarian"},{"data":{"title":"ジャッジ・ドレッド","runtime":0,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":""},"name":"日本語","iso_639_1":"ja","iso_3166_1":"JP","english_name":"Japanese"},{"data":{"title":"Dredd: Ultima judecată","runtime":95,"tagline":"Ziua judecății a sosit.","homepage":"","overview":"Teritoriul Americii în viitor este un deșert nesfârșit. Pe Coasta de Est, începând din Boston și pânâ în Washington DC se întinde Mega Orașul Unu, o metropolă imensă, dominată de violență, unde locuiesc peste 400 de milioane de oameni, într-o teamă perpetuă.  Singurii care încearcă să facă ordine în acest haos urban sunt cei supranumiți Judecătorii. Aceștia reprezintă întregul sistem: oameni ai legii, jurați, judecători și călăi. Cel mai bun dintre Judecători este Dredd, căruia Judecătorul suprem îi dă o misiune. El trebuie să testeze un Judecător începător, pe Cassandra Anderson, care are puteri telepatice. Totul trebuie să fie de fapt ca o zi de instrucție."},"name":"Română","iso_639_1":"ro","iso_3166_1":"RO","english_name":"Romanian"},{"data":{"title":"","runtime":0,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":""},"name":"Bahasa indonesia","iso_639_1":"id","iso_3166_1":"ID","english_name":"Indonesian"},{"data":{"title":"Dredd: O Juiz do Apocalipse","runtime":0,"tagline":"O julgamento está próximo.","homepage":"","overview":"Dredd é um agente da lei responsável por prender, julgar e executar os criminosos de uma megalópole do futuro. Sua missão atual é combater o surgimento de uma nova droga, poderosa e ilegal, além de treinar uma nova recruta com poderes psíquicos."},"name":"Português","iso_639_1":"pt","iso_3166_1":"BR","english_name":"Portuguese"},{"data":{"title":"Суддя Дредд","runtime":0,"tagline":"Правосуддя наближаєтья","homepage":"","overview":"У жорстокому, футуристичному місті за порядок відповідає Міністерство Юстиції, працівники якого, Судді, мають повноваження судді, присяжних та ката. Знаменитий Суддя Дредд разом із стажером потрапляє в лігво банди наркоторговців, які розповсюджують новий наркотик, що змінює реальність, Лета."},"name":"Український","iso_639_1":"uk","iso_3166_1":"UA","english_name":"Ukrainian"},{"data":{"title":"","runtime":95,"tagline":"Le jugement est proche.","homepage":"","overview":"Dans un avenir proche, les États-Unis ne sont plus qu’un immense désert irradié. Mega City One est une métropole tentaculaire rongée par le vice. La seule forme d’autorité restante est représentée par les juges, une police urbaine qui cumule toutes les fonctions : flic, juge et bourreau. Une nouvelle drogue se propage, la Slo-Mo, qui permet de percevoir la réalité au ralenti. Sa distribution est contrôlée par Ma-Ma, ancienne prostituée, devenue baronne de la drogue. Dredd, le juge ultime, va se voir assigner une mission dans les environs de la tour de Ma-Ma et va devoir s’y confronter."},"name":"Français","iso_639_1":"fr","iso_3166_1":"CA","english_name":"French"},{"data":{"title":"超時空戰警3D","runtime":95,"tagline":"審判即將降臨","homepage":"","overview":"未來的美國社會秩序失控，被賦予整治秩序重任的爵德判官與菜鳥卡珊卓，意外踏入由毒販頭子「教母」控制的貧民窟。兩人將不惜代價終結一切罪惡根源，為人民帶來和平的新希望……"},"name":"普通话","iso_639_1":"zh","iso_3166_1":"TW","english_name":"Mandarin"},{"data":{"title":"Dredas","runtime":0,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"Ateityje Amerika virto dykviete, dar žinoma kaip Prakeiktoji Žemė, o jos rytinėje pakrantėje plyti gaujų valdomas, žiaurus ir neaprėpiamas Mega-Miestas Vienas metropolis, kuriame kasdien užfiksuojama 17 000 nusikaltimų. Miesto tvarką palaiko policininkai, turintys teisėjo ir budelio privilegiją. Populiaraus britų komikso herojus Teisėjas Dredas yra vienas iš tokių pareigūnų. Jam ir partnerei, kuriai nepavyko tapti teisėja, patikėta užkirsti kelią sparčiai plintančiam naujam narkotikui. Kol Dredas atlieka budelio prievolę, narkotikų magnatė, žinoma kaip Ma-Ma, pasiunčia žudikus atnešti, jos planus grianančio Teisėjo Dredo galvą."},"name":"Lietuvių","iso_639_1":"lt","iso_3166_1":"LT","english_name":"Lithuanian"},{"data":{"title":"新特警判官","runtime":0,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"2139年，未來世界已被毀滅，罪惡橫行。原本的美國東岸已經成為一個擁有超過8億人口的第一巨城，為了更有制止罪案，當局發展出即捕即審即行刑的罪惡煞星「特警判官」，趕絕一切惡黨兇徒，其中最強皇牌正是德烈 (Dredd)。德烈與擁有超能力的新拍檔姬珊，首日一起行行動已經遇上毒后黨的人馬，更發現三名死者在200層樓高的賊竇「桃樹塔」墮樓身亡。特警判官與毒后大軍重裝對戰一觸即發。"},"name":"普通话","iso_639_1":"zh","iso_3166_1":"HK","english_name":"Mandarin"},{"data":{"title":"Dredd","runtime":0,"tagline":"Juez. Jurado. Ejecutor.","homepage":"","overview":"En un futuro cercano, Norteamérica se ha convertido en un páramo asolado por la radiactividad. Una única y gran megalópolis se extiende a lo largo de la costa este: Mega City 1. Esta inmensa y violenta urbe cuenta con una población de más de 800 millones de personas, cada una de las cuales es un infractor en potencia. Los encargados de acabar con el caos e imponer el orden son unos individuos que actúan a la vez como agentes de la ley, jueces, jurados y verdugos. Al frente de ellos está Dredd (Karl Urban), una leyenda viva de la justicia que vive entregado por entero a hacer cumplir la ley. En una misión aparentemente rutinaria junto a Cassandra Anderson (Olivia Thrilby), una juez novata dotada de grandes habilidades psíquicas, se disponen a investigar un homicidio en un peligroso rascacielos de 200 pisos de altura, controlado por el clan de la despiadada Ma-Ma (Lena Headley)."},"name":"Español","iso_639_1":"es","iso_3166_1":"MX","english_name":"Spanish"},{"data":{"title":"Dredd","runtime":0,"tagline":"Presuda stiže","homepage":"","overview":"Budućnost. Amerika je ozračena pustoš. Na Istočnoj obali, od Bostona do Washingtona prostire se Mega City One - ogromna metropola puna nasilja s više od 400 milijuna prestravljenih stanovnika. Red u urbanom kaosu pokušavaju uvesti samo 'Suci' koji su predstavnici zakona, porotnici, suci i egzekutori - sve u jednome. Među njima se izdvaja - sudac Dredd. Vrhovni sudac šalje ih u misiju - testirati početnicu, moćnu vidovnjakinju Cassandru Anderson. Suci kreću prema naizgled rutinskom ubojstvu u zloglasnom megabloku Peach Trees visokom 200 katova kojeg vodi nemilosrdni klan Ma-Ma. Kad Suci pokušaju uhapsiti jednog od glavnih ubojica klana, Ma-Ma zatvori cijelu zgradu i naredi lov na suce. Dva Dva suca se nađu u opakoj i bespoštednoj borbi za preživljavanje"},"name":"Hrvatski","iso_639_1":"hr","iso_3166_1":"HR","english_name":"Croatian"},{"data":{"title":"","runtime":0,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"Tuleviku Ameerika kujutab endast trööstitut kõnnumaad, mille idarannikul laiub Bostonist Washingtonini Mega City 1 – tohutu, vägivaldne metropol, mille kaootilistel tänavatel valitsevad kurjategijad. Ainsateks seadusesilmadeks on politseinikud, keda kutsutakse Kohtunikeks. Neile antud volitustega on selle üksuse liikmed ühekorraga nii kohtunikeks, vandemeesteks kui ka timukateks. Kohtunike seast kardetuim on Dredd (Karl Urban), kelle ülesandeks on vabastada linn uusimast nuhtlusest, milleks on epideemia mõõtmed võtnud uus uimasti \"Slo-Mo\", mis paneb tarbija kogema reaalsust 100 korda aeglasemalt. Selleks alustab Dredd armutut võitlust endisest prostituudist julma narkokuninganna Ma-Ma'ga (Lena Headey), kelle kindluseks on 200-korruseline \"vertikaalne slumm\", millest reeglina isegi Kohtunikud eemale hoiavad. Aga mitte Dredd..."},"name":"Eesti","iso_639_1":"et","iso_3166_1":"EE","english_name":"Estonian"},{"data":{"title":"","runtime":0,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"Zgodba je postavljena v Ameriko 22. stoletja, ki je le še distopična pustinja. V ogromnem megalopolisu razsaja Ma-Ma, ki z nevarnim novim mamilom namerava zavladati mestu. Ko elitni urbani policist, Sodnik Dredd, z uvajano novinko zaide na njen teritorij v ogromnem bloku, se začne krvavi pregon po temačnih nadstropjih."},"name":"Slovenščina","iso_639_1":"sl","iso_3166_1":"SI","english_name":"Slovenian"}],"reviews_tmdb":[{"id":"50db93c119c29535dbc36f3c","url":"https://www.themoviedb.org/review/50db93c119c29535dbc36f3c","author":"ropesip","content":"I like this movie more than the one with Silvester Stallone. Nice slowmotion shots and a good story for an action movie.","created_at":"2012-12-27T00:18:09.300Z","updated_at":"2021-06-23T15:57:20.487Z","author_details":{"name":"","rating":null,"username":"ropesip","avatar_path":null}},{"id":"50ea1c0d760ee3799412a8d0","url":"https://www.themoviedb.org/review/50ea1c0d760ee3799412a8d0","author":"GeekMasher","content":"This film blow me away! I was not expecting this, a cop (a judge) based in the future with high violent's and great characters. You will think you will hate Dredd but you wont.","created_at":"2013-01-07T00:51:25.071Z","updated_at":"2021-06-23T15:57:20.567Z","author_details":{"name":"","rating":9,"username":"GeekMasher","avatar_path":null}},{"id":"511f69a5760ee35c3b11fb3a","url":"https://www.themoviedb.org/review/511f69a5760ee35c3b11fb3a","author":"Per Gunnar Jonsson","content":"$11","created_at":"2013-02-16T11:12:37.261Z","updated_at":"2024-05-16T15:21:14.213Z","author_details":{"name":"Per Gunnar Jonsson","rating":7,"username":"Dark Jedi","avatar_path":null}},{"id":"5207b0e0760ee362ff24c0b1","url":"https://www.themoviedb.org/review/5207b0e0760ee362ff24c0b1","author":"LastCaress1972","content":"$12","created_at":"2013-08-11T15:42:24.184Z","updated_at":"2021-06-23T15:57:22.134Z","author_details":{"name":"","rating":null,"username":"LastCaress1972","avatar_path":null}},{"id":"5558b043c3a3687774008f3d","url":"https://www.themoviedb.org/review/5558b043c3a3687774008f3d","author":"Andres Gomez","content":"So, nothing new under the sun. The same boring story and characters mixed in another movie. The only thing remarkable in this movie is the slow motion used during the drug usage, which is not much to say.","created_at":"2015-05-17T15:14:11.666Z","updated_at":"2021-06-23T15:57:34.736Z","author_details":{"name":"Andres Gomez","rating":4,"username":"tanty","avatar_path":null}},{"id":"5aaf58d80e0a2665f501f68e","url":"https://www.themoviedb.org/review/5aaf58d80e0a2665f501f68e","author":"Gimly","content":"$13","created_at":"2018-03-19T06:29:44.957Z","updated_at":"2021-06-23T15:58:06.952Z","author_details":{"name":"Gimly","rating":8,"username":"Ruuz","avatar_path":"/xUObnJSvHrFPsIpoDmb1jiQZLq7.jpg"}},{"id":"5c24666192514167fbc64fed","url":"https://www.themoviedb.org/review/5c24666192514167fbc64fed","author":"John Chard","content":"$14","created_at":"2018-12-27T05:42:57.794Z","updated_at":"2024-05-16T15:22:19.848Z","author_details":{"name":"","rating":8,"username":"John Chard","avatar_path":"/utEXl2EDiXBK6f41wCLsvprvMg4.jpg"}},{"id":"623f46d6706e56005dbea1a3","url":"https://www.themoviedb.org/review/623f46d6706e56005dbea1a3","author":"CinemaSerf","content":"$15","created_at":"2022-03-26T17:01:10.708Z","updated_at":"2022-03-26T17:01:10.708Z","author_details":{"name":"CinemaSerf","rating":null,"username":"Geronimo1967","avatar_path":"/9HcQx0Yfbxy8eqr3ft66X9uWMf0.jpg"}}],"recommendations":[{"id":9482,"adult":false,"title":"Judge Dredd","video":false,"overview":"In a dystopian future, Dredd, the most famous judge (a cop with instant field judiciary powers) is convicted for a crime he did not commit while his murderous counterpart escapes.","genre_ids":[878,28],"media_type":"movie","popularity":5.6706,"vote_count":2662,"poster_path":"/cfSnKn8NDU3m8UxihjVcYprA0Aq.jpg","release_date":"1995-06-30","vote_average":5.844,"backdrop_path":"/baJHUXBcoaHnMf2sjwegbuhIjEV.jpg","original_title":"Judge Dredd","original_language":"en"},{"id":64635,"adult":false,"title":"Total Recall","video":false,"overview":"Factory worker Doug Quaid takes a virtual mind-trip vacation with the Rekall company, opting for implanted memories of being a spy. When the procedure goes wrong, Quaid becomes a wanted man by the police and joins forces with a rebel fighter to stop the evil Chancellor Cohaagen.","genre_ids":[28,878,53],"media_type":"movie","popularity":5.3648,"vote_count":5774,"poster_path":"/hVUxVVzZ0WvvPIpKwsMPMDOQyqi.jpg","release_date":"2012-08-02","vote_average":6.025,"backdrop_path":"/uBHeAB2Ug9ELBzkMyls8CUjzn4i.jpg","original_title":"Total Recall","original_language":"en"},{"id":71679,"adult":false,"title":"Resident Evil: Retribution","video":false,"overview":"The Umbrella Corporation’s deadly T-virus continues to ravage the Earth, transforming the global population into legions of the flesh eating Undead. The human race’s last and only hope, Alice, awakens in the heart of Umbrella’s most clandestine operations facility and unveils more of her mysterious past as she delves further into the complex. Without a safe haven, Alice continues to hunt those responsible for the outbreak; a chase that takes her from Tokyo to New York, Washington, D.C. and Moscow, culminating in a mind-blowing revelation that will force her to rethink everything that she once thought to be true. Aided by new found allies and familiar friends, Alice must fight to survive long enough to escape a hostile world on the brink of oblivion. The countdown has begun.","genre_ids":[28,27,878],"media_type":"movie","popularity":0.6025,"vote_count":4234,"poster_path":"/ohdUDWVlcbuWphaLu6wS91xdJ73.jpg","release_date":"2012-09-12","vote_average":5.834,"backdrop_path":"/mLgFebdy051NX1vfFrpuUPRQHgg.jpg","original_title":"Resident Evil: Retribution","original_language":"en"},{"id":8681,"adult":false,"title":"Taken","video":false,"overview":"Bryan Mills, a former government operative, is trying to reconnect with his teenage daughter Kim. After reluctantly agreeing with his ex-wife to let Kim go to Paris on vacation with a friend, his worst nightmare comes true. While on the phone with his daughter shortly after she arrives in Paris, she and her friend are abducted by a gang of human traffickers. Working against the clock, Bryan relies on his extensive training and skills to track down the ruthless gang that abducted her and launch a one-man war to rescue his daughter.","genre_ids":[28,53],"media_type":"movie","popularity":11.6476,"vote_count":11887,"poster_path":"/ognkaUSNgJe1a2pjB4UNdzEo5jT.jpg","release_date":"2008-02-18","vote_average":7.4,"backdrop_path":"/lMRMjd9yJsZLyaT97eiURu2zVb4.jpg","original_title":"Taken","original_language":"en"},{"id":116613,"adult":false,"title":"The Sweeney","video":false,"overview":"Jack Regan, a hardened cop who doesn’t play by the rules, is confronted with a criminal from his past. With sidekick George Carter they are put on the case of a jewellery store heist that ends in a killing. But is that killing really an execution in disguise? With pressure from his boss and the fact that Regan is having an affair with that boss’s wife, it’s not going to be easy for him to stay out of trouble.","genre_ids":[28,80],"media_type":"movie","popularity":1.3797,"vote_count":289,"poster_path":"/nwGo7AoYXG4C03wbyfdeYvcVbnV.jpg","release_date":"2012-09-11","vote_average":5.744,"backdrop_path":"/mfYG7D6fQdnKopR6DqnXyfkWG8W.jpg","original_title":"The Sweeney","original_language":"en"},{"id":88005,"adult":false,"title":"Seeking a Friend for the End of the World","video":false,"overview":"As an asteroid nears Earth, a man finds himself alone after his wife leaves in a panic. He decides to take a road trip to reunite with his high school sweetheart. Accompanying him is a neighbor who inadvertently puts a wrench in his plan.","genre_ids":[35,18,10749,12],"media_type":"movie","popularity":1.4552,"vote_count":2214,"poster_path":"/rBbCwFLyt7Q25yaw2bEOQh7RMG1.jpg","release_date":"2012-06-22","vote_average":6.565,"backdrop_path":"/tEJ3nvnp520AvNPbhCegHMo1EfM.jpg","original_title":"Seeking a Friend for the End of the World","original_language":"en"},{"id":64690,"adult":false,"title":"Drive","video":false,"overview":"Driver is a skilled Hollywood stuntman who moonlights as a getaway driver for criminals. Though he projects an icy exterior, lately he's been warming up to a pretty neighbor named Irene and her young son, Benicio. When Irene's husband gets out of jail, he enlists Driver's help in a million-dollar heist. The job goes horribly wrong, and Driver must risk his life to protect Irene and Benicio from the vengeful masterminds behind the robbery.","genre_ids":[18,53,80],"media_type":"movie","popularity":7.8036,"vote_count":13369,"poster_path":"/602vevIURmpDfzbnv5Ubi6wIkQm.jpg","release_date":"2011-09-15","vote_average":7.582,"backdrop_path":"/iymDDg4upZWgpbSeiE1JCjsSPBs.jpg","original_title":"Drive","original_language":"en"},{"id":329,"adult":false,"title":"Jurassic Park","video":false,"overview":"A wealthy entrepreneur secretly creates a theme park featuring living dinosaurs drawn from prehistoric DNA. Before opening day, he invites a team of experts and his two eager grandchildren to experience the park and help calm anxious investors. However, the park is anything but amusing as the security systems go off-line and the dinosaurs escape.","genre_ids":[12,878],"media_type":"movie","popularity":8.0903,"vote_count":17539,"poster_path":"/maFjKnJ62hDQ9E66dKqDZgbUy0H.jpg","release_date":"1993-06-11","vote_average":7.965,"backdrop_path":"/alqZDg4DXBpNCVTzRPXe5zkkAXX.jpg","original_title":"Jurassic Park","original_language":"en"},{"id":58574,"adult":false,"title":"Sherlock Holmes: A Game of Shadows","video":false,"overview":"There is a new criminal mastermind at large (Professor Moriarty) and not only is he Holmes’ intellectual equal, but his capacity for evil and lack of conscience may give him an advantage over the  detective.","genre_ids":[12,28,80,9648],"media_type":"movie","popularity":3.9311,"vote_count":10799,"poster_path":"/vskIKrMNUAhns05dx8WYBQfcJEs.jpg","release_date":"2011-11-22","vote_average":7.142,"backdrop_path":"/e3Myaqo4krqeeh4UkssAEISjIgh.jpg","original_title":"Sherlock Holmes: A Game of Shadows","original_language":"en"},{"id":59967,"adult":false,"title":"Looper","video":false,"overview":"In the year 2044, time travel has not yet been invented but in 30 years it will have been. When the mob wants to get rid of someone, they will send their target into the past where a looper, a hired gun, like Joe is waiting to mop up. Joe is getting rich and life is good until the day the mob decides to close the loop, sending back Joe's future self for assassination.","genre_ids":[28,53,878],"media_type":"movie","popularity":7.4019,"vote_count":10694,"poster_path":"/sNjL6SqErDBE8OUZlrDLkexfsCj.jpg","release_date":"2012-09-26","vote_average":6.901,"backdrop_path":"/4GPCnwvTbsDleH5QIOyDLMsK8a2.jpg","original_title":"Looper","original_language":"en"},{"id":1534,"adult":false,"title":"Pathfinder","video":false,"overview":"A Viking boy is left behind after his clan battles a Native American tribe. Raised within the tribe, he ultimately becomes their savior in a fight against the Norsemen.","genre_ids":[12,28],"media_type":"movie","popularity":1.6466,"vote_count":760,"poster_path":"/mME7efKNTU7jzXTgFkI1t0aQUiz.jpg","release_date":"2007-01-11","vote_average":5.666,"backdrop_path":"/x1iHrvnxB3IuNBiTvqdfQqeh2mk.jpg","original_title":"Pathfinder","original_language":"en"},{"id":1662,"adult":false,"title":"State of Grace","video":false,"overview":"Hell's Kitchen, New York. Terry Noonan returns home after a ten-year absence. He soon reconnects with Jackie, a childhood friend and member of the Irish mob, and rekindles his love affair with Jackie's sister Kathleen.","genre_ids":[18,80,53],"media_type":"movie","popularity":1.2524,"vote_count":400,"poster_path":"/dNMeRLY3MeY2FFeh639plHai3F1.jpg","release_date":"1990-09-14","vote_average":6.9,"backdrop_path":"/rQfoRwxlkU8hdUnruoicnCuc4XO.jpg","original_title":"State of Grace","original_language":"en"},{"id":20504,"adult":false,"title":"The Book of Eli","video":false,"overview":"A post-apocalyptic tale, in which a lone man fights his way across America in order to protect a sacred book that holds the secrets to saving humankind.","genre_ids":[28,53,878],"media_type":"movie","popularity":7.2806,"vote_count":6542,"poster_path":"/1H1y9ZiqNFaLgQiRDDZLA55PviW.jpg","release_date":"2010-01-14","vote_average":6.792,"backdrop_path":"/aPrrrGtSjXbw8XnpzsVJgF0ioq3.jpg","original_title":"The Book of Eli","original_language":"en"},{"id":77016,"adult":false,"title":"End of Watch","video":false,"overview":"Two young officers are marked for death after confiscating a small cache of money and firearms from the members of a notorious cartel during a routine traffic stop.","genre_ids":[80,18,53],"media_type":"movie","popularity":4.1505,"vote_count":3529,"poster_path":"/pDeVKQICkcdwwjHxGj0MeS14YJ6.jpg","release_date":"2012-09-20","vote_average":7.349,"backdrop_path":"/l53K8Fp1WcOMRL33CMsnnMUPiWg.jpg","original_title":"End of Watch","original_language":"en"},{"id":106021,"adult":false,"title":"Erased","video":false,"overview":"A former agent of the CIA and his estranged daughter go on the run after his employers target them for assassination.","genre_ids":[28,53],"media_type":"movie","popularity":1.7799,"vote_count":778,"poster_path":"/42OvgvP795xTfVINk48PAYWEFt7.jpg","release_date":"2012-08-23","vote_average":6.1,"backdrop_path":"/cOEd8b4lBqVIriNTMuhEi3nelZC.jpg","original_title":"Erased","original_language":"en"},{"id":75780,"adult":false,"title":"Jack Reacher","video":false,"overview":"One morning in an ordinary town, five people are shot dead in a seemingly random attack. All evidence points to a single suspect: an ex-military sniper who is quickly brought into custody. The interrogation yields one written note: 'Get Jack Reacher!'. Reacher, an enigmatic ex-Army investigator, believes the authorities have the right man but agrees to help the sniper's defense attorney. However, the more Reacher delves into the case, the less clear-cut it appears. So begins an extraordinary chase for the truth, pitting Jack Reacher against an unexpected enemy, with a skill for violence and a secret to keep.","genre_ids":[80,18,53,28],"media_type":"movie","popularity":7.442,"vote_count":7492,"poster_path":"/uQBbjrLVsUibWxNDGA4Czzo8lwz.jpg","release_date":"2012-12-20","vote_average":6.653,"backdrop_path":"/iwvP8XVpYVmJ3xfF9xdBi5uAOWl.jpg","original_title":"Jack Reacher","original_language":"en"},{"id":23483,"adult":false,"title":"Kick-Ass","video":false,"overview":"Dave Lizewski is an unnoticed high school student and comic book fan who one day decides to become a super-hero, even though he has no powers, training or meaningful reason to do so.","genre_ids":[28,80],"media_type":"movie","popularity":8.3776,"vote_count":12201,"poster_path":"/iHMbrTHJwocsNvo5murCBw0CwTo.jpg","release_date":"2010-03-26","vote_average":7.122,"backdrop_path":"/P4bGyJQF0shAcRku3I2perNUQR.jpg","original_title":"Kick-Ass","original_language":"en"},{"id":98357,"adult":false,"title":"Broken City","video":false,"overview":"In a broken city rife with injustice, ex-cop Billy Taggart seeks redemption and revenge after being double-crossed and then framed by its most powerful figure, the mayor. Billy's relentless pursuit of justice, matched only by his streetwise toughness, makes him an unstoppable force - and the mayor's worst nightmare.","genre_ids":[53,80,18],"media_type":"movie","popularity":6.2881,"vote_count":1548,"poster_path":"/hqa5FwNZC55zqSpdeGFtBDqw55y.jpg","release_date":"2013-01-18","vote_average":5.949,"backdrop_path":"/lZ9OGovrjamAVz3n6TjJts2npxE.jpg","original_title":"Broken City","original_language":"en"},{"id":68179,"adult":false,"title":"Escape from Planet Earth","video":false,"overview":"Astronaut Scorch Supernova finds himself caught in a trap when he responds to an SOS from a notoriously dangerous alien planet.","genre_ids":[16,35,12,10751,878],"media_type":"movie","popularity":1.662,"vote_count":797,"poster_path":"/9la0CSCJqwh6io3yk4Xv3aEZxEA.jpg","release_date":"2013-02-14","vote_average":5.752,"backdrop_path":"/dlReM2zDrOfkvrJj9R96XmhNdS4.jpg","original_title":"Escape from Planet Earth","original_language":"en"},{"id":49529,"adult":false,"title":"John Carter","video":false,"overview":"John Carter is a war-weary, former military captain who's inexplicably transported to the mysterious and exotic planet of Barsoom (Mars) and reluctantly becomes embroiled in an epic conflict. It's a world on the brink of collapse, and Carter rediscovers his humanity when he realizes the survival of Barsoom and its people rests in his hands.","genre_ids":[28,12,878],"media_type":"movie","popularity":5.3366,"vote_count":5988,"poster_path":"/lCxz1Yus07QCQQCb6I0Dr3Lmqpx.jpg","release_date":"2012-03-07","vote_average":6.355,"backdrop_path":"/hj5RynBrJB1Wlz84t3lJj9DuTJh.jpg","original_title":"John Carter","original_language":"en"}],"similar_content":[{"id":155,"adult":false,"title":"The Dark Knight","video":false,"overview":"Batman raises the stakes in his war on crime. With the help of Lt. Jim Gordon and District Attorney Harvey Dent, Batman sets out to dismantle the remaining criminal organizations that plague the streets. The partnership proves to be effective, but they soon find themselves prey to a reign of chaos unleashed by a rising criminal mastermind known to the terrified citizens of Gotham as the Joker.","genre_ids":[28,80,53],"popularity":29.0324,"vote_count":35204,"poster_path":"/qJ2tW6WMUDux911r6m7haRef0WH.jpg","release_date":"2008-07-16","vote_average":8.526,"backdrop_path":"/dqK9Hag1054tghRQSqLSfrkvQnA.jpg","original_title":"The Dark Knight","original_language":"en"},{"id":158,"adult":false,"title":"Knockin' on Heaven's Door","video":false,"overview":"Two young men, Martin and Rudi, both suffering from terminal cancer, get to know each other in a hospital room. They drown their desperation in tequila and decide to take one last trip to the sea. Drunk and still in pajamas they steal the first fancy car they find, a 60's Mercedes convertible. The car happens to belong to a bunch of gangsters, which immediately start to chase it, since it contains more than the pistol Martin finds in the glove box.","genre_ids":[35,80,28,18],"popularity":1.4976,"vote_count":570,"poster_path":"/dsY09zCxKDFjfV1oqXFJJpVrHdP.jpg","release_date":"1997-02-20","vote_average":7.69,"backdrop_path":"/yXnlw2SB0QhYUC4QDyuRZh3CQlU.jpg","original_title":"Knockin' on Heaven's Door","original_language":"de"},{"id":170,"adult":false,"title":"28 Days Later","video":false,"overview":"Twenty-eight days after a killer virus was accidentally unleashed from a British research facility, a small group of London survivors are caught in a desperate struggle to protect themselves from the infected. Carried by animals and humans, the virus turns those it infects into homicidal maniacs -- and it's absolutely impossible to contain.","genre_ids":[27,53,878],"popularity":16.2528,"vote_count":8235,"poster_path":"/sQckQRt17VaWbo39GIu0TMOiszq.jpg","release_date":"2002-10-31","vote_average":7.237,"backdrop_path":"/aJFwk1clMal1prxAvKAgHxKPAf.jpg","original_title":"28 Days Later","original_language":"en"},{"id":180,"adult":false,"title":"Minority Report","video":false,"overview":"John Anderton is a top 'Precrime' cop in the late-21st century, when technology can predict crimes before they're committed. But Anderton becomes the quarry when another investigator targets him for a murder charge.","genre_ids":[878,28,53],"popularity":6.7464,"vote_count":9404,"poster_path":"/ccqpHq5tk5W4ymbSbuoy4uYOxFI.jpg","release_date":"2002-06-20","vote_average":7.349,"backdrop_path":"/PrMb3oeEluauy0q9ZO5xL33A6C.jpg","original_title":"Minority Report","original_language":"en"},{"id":185,"adult":false,"title":"A Clockwork Orange","video":false,"overview":"In a near-future Britain, young Alexander DeLarge and his pals get their kicks beating and raping anyone they please. When not destroying the lives of others, Alex swoons to the music of Beethoven. The state, eager to crack down on juvenile crime, gives an incarcerated Alex the option to undergo an invasive procedure that'll rob him of all personal agency. In a time when conscience is a commodity, can Alex change his tune?","genre_ids":[878,80],"popularity":9.2739,"vote_count":13612,"poster_path":"/4sHeTAp65WrSSuc05nRBKddhBxO.jpg","release_date":"1971-10-28","vote_average":8.18,"backdrop_path":"/nLFxvLokHe3bQmrmAfljIfax2jQ.jpg","original_title":"A Clockwork Orange","original_language":"en"},{"id":189,"adult":false,"title":"Sin City: A Dame to Kill For","video":false,"overview":"Some of Sin City's most hard-boiled citizens cross paths with a few of its more reviled inhabitants.","genre_ids":[28,80,53],"popularity":4.8151,"vote_count":4077,"poster_path":"/50kALxDX4mmzIRljbNbPY0u4cie.jpg","release_date":"2014-08-20","vote_average":6.402,"backdrop_path":"/rxMnmklIpunsNsRkQ7hw61ZJa84.jpg","original_title":"Sin City: A Dame to Kill For","original_language":"en"},{"id":590003,"adult":false,"title":"A Living Dog","video":false,"overview":"The war between mankind and intelligent machines has begun - and the machines are winning. Tomasz is a deserter who tries to hide as far away from the battle as possible.  In the vast emptiness of northern Scandinavia he meets Lilja, the last survivor of a resistance group, who is determined to fight the superior machines. With every minute that passes the machines get closer, searching for the last remains of the human race. And the enemy doesn't just shoot on sight - their perfect sensors are programmed to recognize human voice patterns.  So if you speak or even whisper - you die.","genre_ids":[878,28,53],"popularity":0.1779,"vote_count":3,"poster_path":"/kkpeYDMS0LPLPtQveJGvkLMk4V8.jpg","release_date":"2019-09-07","vote_average":5.3,"backdrop_path":"/eECrrbuwrf4Xjc6i5rLv3yijMjV.jpg","original_title":"A Living Dog","original_language":"en"},{"id":590223,"adult":false,"title":"Love and Monsters","video":false,"overview":"Seven years since the Monsterpocalypse began, Joel Dawson has been living underground in order to survive. But after reconnecting over radio with his high school girlfriend Aimee, Joel decides to venture out to reunite with her, despite all the dangerous monsters that stand in his way.","genre_ids":[35,12,878],"popularity":4.0296,"vote_count":4347,"poster_path":"/718NnyxyQuBQcGWt9sdelA1Zc3h.jpg","release_date":"2020-10-16","vote_average":7.275,"backdrop_path":"/lA5fOBqTOQBQ1s9lEYYPmNXoYLi.jpg","original_title":"Love and Monsters","original_language":"en"},{"id":419261,"adult":false,"title":"Earthtastrophe","video":false,"overview":"In a white hot flash of light, and with no warning, one minute our moon is there, the next it's gone. Then, a second flash. And that's the last thing anyone on Earth can remember. 11 months later, it's not post- apocalyptic; it's apocalyptic as Earth has been sucked through a wormhole, literally ripping our planet from the inside out. With bizarre disasters and civilization collapsing, our heroes must find a way to survive and get to \"safe ground\" before it's too late.","genre_ids":[878,10770],"popularity":2.667,"vote_count":44,"poster_path":"/PdO6DOQktCGtPeZRrtOZhtvjWf.jpg","release_date":"2016-03-05","vote_average":4.6,"backdrop_path":"/q9VrDrEO55HppFzEchAmHfGH1Qw.jpg","original_title":"Earthtastrophe","original_language":"en"},{"id":947924,"adult":false,"title":"Běžci","video":false,"overview":"After the global collapse of civilization, part of Europe remains uninhabitable. People form small groups, surviving in safe zones separated from each other by strips of land where uncontrolled military technology creates deadly \"traps.\" The only ones who can cross the dangerous territories are the \"runners.\" The fate of several people who have decided to find a safe place for a new life depends on one of them.","genre_ids":[878,18],"popularity":0.171,"vote_count":1,"poster_path":null,"release_date":"2014-04-23","vote_average":6,"backdrop_path":null,"original_title":"Běžci","original_language":"cs"},{"id":1291785,"adult":false,"title":"Twilight of the Warriors: Dragon Throne","video":false,"overview":"The second installment of the Twilight of the Warriors trilogy.\r In 1950s Hong Kong, brothers Lui Cheng-tung and Chen Jim fled to the lawless Kowloon Walled City at the peak of their careers. They endured hardships, waiting for a chance to reclaim their losses. During this time, they encountered a man who significantly influenced their struggle to regain what they had lost.","genre_ids":[28,53,80,12],"popularity":0.7488,"vote_count":0,"poster_path":"/5D4Ss05hIbV7E8fjO4ZThLbGa6J.jpg","release_date":"","vote_average":0,"backdrop_path":null,"o